title: #67: The Manliness of Jack London With Earle Labor
description: I talk to Jack London scholar Earle Labor about his new biography on Jack London entitled, Jack London: An American Life. Professor Labor and I talk about what Jack London can teach men about being men and how his life and work can inspire adventure even today.
author: contact@artofmanliness.com (The Art of Manliness)
